--INSTALL--

To install:
1. Download the scripts and configuration ini.
2. Modify the config ini to suit your setup
	a. IP of your limitlessLED controller (wifi bridge)
	b. Type of bulbs you have (only RGBW commands are currently present)
	c. Dim interval if you want to change it
	d. Which type of things to do for (TV and Movies are supported)
3. Copy all three files onto your Kodi host @ ~/
4. Move autoexec.py to your userdata folder (~/.kodi/userdata/)
5. Move playeractions.py and the ini into the scripts folder (~/.kodi/scripts/)
6. Restart kodi to initialise the scripts
